{
  "stem": "9.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I started on the journey to various camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I do have to tell now what was the difference between a work camp and a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I was in two concentration camps, Auschwitz, the famous one, and Bergen-Belsen, and in four work camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "As I mentioned before my muscles, that's where my muscles came in very handy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I-- they could see that I'm a good worker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They could see that they could use me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My muscles were showing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And here I was, always transferred to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "After a couple work camps, which was, Plaszow and Elsnig-- Plaszow is a famous camp where was made-- I landed in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I have a tattoo on my left hand and the number is A14821.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Everybody got a tattoo and that was our name.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The number was the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "In Auschwitz, immediately they shaved our hair, took away the clothes that I had.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was given a sack, like a potato sack, with cut out two holes for arms and one for my head, no underwear, and some kind of wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They weren't really shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I looked horrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When I looked at other people, we looked like walking skeletons.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "After my hair grew about half-inch, a cross was shaved across my head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And then I looked like a monkey, because I had some stubs of hair sticking out on the sides, but in the middle, I was shaved.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I personally did not see Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Mengele in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But I have heard from the many witnesses about all the experiments that he was doing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He was doing experiments on skins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I mean, they were all inhuman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But there he had, instead of using guinea pigs for medical experiments, he was using human beings.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
